1
00:00:00,334 --> 00:00:02,250
Name: Rayan Riyad Khalil

2
00:00:03,125 --> 00:00:04,876
Born in 1987

3
00:00:05,292 --> 00:00:07,083
I was detained in Ras al-Kour

4
00:00:08,209 --> 00:00:12,542
Three people came in a <i>Hisba</i> vehicle

5
00:00:13,918 --> 00:00:16,042
And they brought us to this place

6
00:00:16,876 --> 00:00:17,959
Interviewer: What was the reason for the detention?

7
00:00:18,042 --> 00:00:20,876
The first detention was because of prayer

8
00:00:22,167 --> 00:00:26,667
And the second detention was because of people and belongings we were taking out of the town

9
00:00:27,417 --> 00:00:32,959
So they focused on me and started monitoring me

10
00:00:33,459 --> 00:00:35,250
The second time they brought me to this place

11
00:00:35,834 --> 00:00:37,250
Interviewer: What is your job?

12
00:00:37,292 --> 00:00:39,417
I worked as a cargo truck driver on the Turkey route

13
00:00:40,083 --> 00:00:41,834
Interviewer: Do you mean a medicine truck?

14
00:00:41,876 --> 00:00:43,667
A passenger car, we would take people and bring them

15
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:48,042
They used to say this area has <i>Rafida</i> [Shia]

16
00:00:48,042 --> 00:00:51,292
And they brought us in under this pretext

17
00:00:52,375 --> 00:00:53,584
Interviewer: Were you married?

18
00:00:53,609 --> 00:00:54,809
Yes, I was married

19
00:00:54,834 --> 00:00:56,959
Interviewer: How many children do you have? Witness: Three

20
00:00:58,459 --> 00:01:01,667
Interviewer: When did they arrest you, and what were you doing?

21
00:01:02,083 --> 00:01:05,542
And how many people were there when they brought you to this place?

22
00:01:05,584 --> 00:01:08,542
They were three people

23
00:01:08,792 --> 00:01:11,167
They brought us into this place

24
00:01:13,918 --> 00:01:16,000
There was an information desk inside

25
00:01:17,167 --> 00:01:23,125
There was an information desk, and then we went in

26
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:28,584
Interviewer: While they were bringing you here

27
00:01:28,792 --> 00:01:31,959
Interviewer: Did they insult you or beat you? Witness: No

28
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:37,626
But I did not know what my fate would be or why they had brought me here
